Compute msec since the Unix Epoch

h2o.mktime(year = 1970, month = 0, day = 0, hour = 0, minute = 0,
  second = 0, msec = 0)

Arguments

year

Defaults to 1970
month

zero based (months are 0 to 11)
day

zero based (days are 0 to 30)
hour

hour
minute

minute
second

second
msec

msec
